<lb n="0903c13" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0903002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說大吉祥陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0903c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0903c15" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0903003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0903003"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西</rdg></app>天<note n="0903004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0903004"><lem wit="【大】">譯經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0903c16" ed="T"/>明教大師<note n="0903005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0903005"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0903c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0903c1701">如是我聞。一時佛在蘇珂&CB00085;帝佛剎。與諸大
<lb n="0903c18" ed="T"/>菩薩并部多眾俱。爾時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。
<lb n="0903c19" ed="T"/>來詣佛所到已頭面禮足於一面坐。復有菩
<lb n="0903c20" ed="T"/>薩摩訶薩名大吉祥。亦詣佛所到已繞佛三
<lb n="0903c21" ed="T"/>匝。頭面禮足&CB00230;坐一面。</p>
<lb n="0903c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0903c2201">爾時世尊見大吉祥菩薩已。告觀自在菩薩
<lb n="0903c23" ed="T"/>言。此大吉祥菩薩有陀羅尼。若閻浮提濁惡
<lb n="0903c24" ed="T"/>世中。有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷等。見聞
<lb n="0903c25" ed="T"/>隨喜讀誦受持。信解此法思惟記念。是貧苦
<lb n="0903c26" ed="T"/>者獲大富貴。乃至部多普令愛敬。如是功德
<lb n="0903c27" ed="T"/>不可具說。時觀自在菩薩聞佛<note n="0903006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">語＝說【明】</note><app n="0903006"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">說</rdg></app>已。歡喜踊
<lb n="0903c28" ed="T"/>躍即從座起。合掌白佛言。世尊我今樂聞。唯
<lb n="0903c29" ed="T"/>願世尊為我宣說。</p>
<pb n="0904a" id="T21.1381.0904a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0904a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904a0101">爾時世尊即說大吉祥陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0904a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904a0201" type="dharani">怛&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身下同</note>他<note place="inline">引一</note>洛叱彌<note place="inline">二合二</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;捺彌
<lb n="0904a03" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;呬抳<note place="inline">引三</note>馱曩<note place="inline">引</note>提&CB00425;底<note place="inline">引四</note>藕哩<note place="inline">引五</note>摩
<lb n="0904a04" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note>野舍<note place="inline">引六</note>&CB00425;捺摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;怛哩<note place="inline">二合七</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0904a05" ed="T"/>&CB00135;喻<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">八</note>案曩那<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">九</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉
<lb n="0904a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>婆摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合十</note>婆野替<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">十一</note>屹哩
<lb n="0904a07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;屹哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">十二</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>遏迦哩也
<lb n="0904a08" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>爍彌<note place="inline">引十三</note>提&CB00135;提&CB00135;<note place="inline">十四</note>悉悉悉悉<note place="inline">十五</note>&CB00135;
<lb n="0904a09" ed="T"/>底&CB00135;底<note place="inline">十六</note>呬&CB00135;呬&CB00135;<note place="inline">十七</note>阿洛叉彌<note place="inline">二合十八</note>彌曩
<lb n="0904a10" ed="T"/>舍野<note place="inline">十九</note>薩&CB00085;洛叉彌<note place="inline">二合</note>彌娑&CB00833;<note place="inline">切身引</note>那野莎
<lb n="0904a11" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">二十</note>曩莫薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">二十一</note>冒提薩怛
<lb n="0904a12" ed="T"/>吠<note place="inline">二合引</note>毘野<note place="inline">二合</note>莎<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引二十二</note></p>
<lb n="0904a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0904a1301">爾時世尊說是經已。觀自在菩薩大吉祥菩
<lb n="0904a14" ed="T"/>薩。并諸菩薩及部多眾。聞佛所說皆大歡喜
<lb n="0904a15" ed="T"/>信受奉行。</p>
<lb n="0904a16" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說大吉祥陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
